{"tid":866022,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解見到太陽會打乞嗤","createTime":"2018-10-17T14:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T03:36:11.000Z","uid":29836,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"21799695feae0d2d46a94bb3ccdcbbfda1de79b1","tid":866022,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人都係咁？"},{"pid":"b98d6067b488d8c3c5d1e5b19654bc63dcb25d33","tid":866022,"uid":48889,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:10:39.000Z","msg":"一出去有陽光嘅地方一定會打一個<br />\n由細到大都係咁 唔知點解"},{"pid":"04f6714abd33e4743570694d9b8e7b43fbbfc1dc","tid":866022,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:16:15.000Z","msg":"六環彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27599da9c0d226f9ff1e7687fe2736c6a481b6dc","tid":866022,"uid":115170,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:16:34.000Z","msg":"有個講法係原始人住係山洞入面<br />\n如果係山洞入面打乞嗤會傳染病菌俾同伴<br />\n所以進化到出洞見太陽先打"},{"pid":"3af3035f5dd813d4236f368b51f5232e661ca8bc","tid":866022,"uid":35668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:17:57.000Z","msg":"因為太陽像大紅花"},{"pid":"da967cb535eba498834ec0ac793adc1c11344927","tid":866022,"uid":25635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:18:49.000Z","msg":"我見由好暗去到有光/忽然比閃光燈斬都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a657a6626816a9d66024ba4614096e6af70e4a10","tid":866022,"uid":155067,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:22:12.000Z","msg":"太陽刺激到眼球<br />\n大腦接收視網膜訊號時，臉部三叉神經也接到。由於大腦誤以為鼻子也受到刺激，所以作出打乞嗤的反應。"},{"pid":"bc88f00c7e9eba09e97ed1ce5e7162307d2d9167","tid":866022,"uid":10296,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:37:16.000Z","msg":"Photic sneeze reflex"},{"pid":"60e7556d47217367ef9f15d8f2e3953daf8298ca","tid